import React from 'react'
import {StyledWrapper,CheckoutImageContainer,
    CheckoutImage,CheckoutName,CheckoutRemove,CheckoutQuantity,CheckoutPrice} from './styles'

const CheckoutItem = ({item}) => (
    <StyledWrapper>
      <CheckoutImageContainer>
          <CheckoutImage alt="item" src={item.imageUrl}/>
      </CheckoutImageContainer>
      <CheckoutName>{item.name}</CheckoutName>
      <CheckoutQuantity>{item.quantity}</CheckoutQuantity>
      <CheckoutPrice>{item.price * item.quantity}</CheckoutPrice>
      <CheckoutRemove>
        &#10005
      </CheckoutRemove>
    </StyledWrapper>
  )



export default CheckoutItem;
